OL,3,CMedical professionals say 'greater
OL,4,Cclarity' needed over assisted dying
OL,5,CBills
OL,7,FMedical professionals insist "greater
OL,8,Fclarity" is needed about Bills at both
OL,9,FWestminster and Holyrood that would
OL,10,Flegalise assisted dying for terminally
OL,11,Fill adults.
OL,13,FThe Royal College of Physicians and
OL,14,FSurgeons of Glasgow spoke out after
OL,15,Fsurveying members across the UK on the
OL,16,Fpracticalities of implementing
OL,17,Fassisted dying, should the legislation
OL,18,Fbe passed.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@HO]
