OL,7,FAlmost half (48%) said assessing a
OL,8,Fpatient's capacity to request an
OL,9,Fassisted death could also be a "major
OL,10,Fchallenge".
OL,12,FMeanwhile 45% said they had "major
OL,13,Fconcerns" about how terminal illness
OL,14,Fis defined in MSP Liam McArthur's
OL,15,FAssisted Dying for Terminally Ill
OL,16,FAdults (Scotland) ` with 40% having
OL,17,F"major concerns" about this in MP Kim
OL,18,FLeadbeater's Bill, which would apply
OL,19,Fin England and Wales.
