OL,7,FPhysicians, surgeons and dental
OL,8,Fsurgeons all took part in the
OL,9,Fresearch, along with GPs, nurses and
OL,10,Fallied health professionals.
OL,12,FIt comes as a record number of
OL,13,Famendments means that further time has
OL,14,Fhad to be scheduled in the House of
OL,15,FLords for Ms Leadbeater's Terminally
OL,16,FIll Adults (End of Life) Bill.
