OL,5,CBills
OL,7,F"However, with two Bills currently
OL,8,Funder discussion, it was important for
OL,9,Fus to ask our members for their views
OL,10,Fon the practicalities of implementing
OL,11,Fthe Bills should they become law."
OL,13,FShe continued: "While doctors and
OL,14,Fhealthcare professionals have a range
OL,15,Fof views on the principle of assisted
OL,16,Fdying, all are deeply concerned for
OL,17,Fthe wellbeing of their patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]uD@POU
