OL,5,CBills
OL,7,F"The survey has shown that if the
OL,8,FBills were to become law, there is a
OL,9,Fstrong need for greater clarity to
OL,10,Fprotect both patients and doctors."
OL,12,FDr McElroy said: "Respondents to the
OL,13,Fsurvey were particularly concerned
OL,14,Fabout the challenges of assessing
OL,15,Fwhether a patient has made their
OL,16,Fdecision voluntarily, and their
OL,17,Fcapacity to make that decision.
