OL,3,CMedical professionals say 'greater
OL,4,Cclarity' needed over assisted dying
OL,5,CBills
OL,7,F"They also told us that greater
OL,8,Fclarity would be needed on the role of
OL,9,Fthe clinician and their right to
OL,10,Fchoose whether to take part in an
OL,11,Fassisted dying service, along with
OL,12,Fsafeguards for people with
OL,13,Fdisabilities and current workforce
OL,14,Fpreparedness, and the impact on
OL,15,Fpalliative care services."
OL,17,FShe added: "These are complex issues
OL,18,Fthat require particularly careful
OL,19,Fconsideration and discussion."
