OL,7,FLiam McArthur MSP said: "I thank the
OL,8,FRCPSG for their work on assisted dying
OL,9,Fand am pleased to note that a
OL,10,Fsignificant number of clinicians who
OL,11,Ftook part in the survey are supportive
OL,12,Fof my Bill.
