OL,3,CMedical professionals say 'greater
OL,4,Cclarity' needed over assisted dying
OL,5,CBills
OL,7,F"These include clarifying that a
OL,8,Fperson is not terminally ill only
OL,9,Fbecause they have a disability or
OL,10,Fmental disorder, that doctors can
OL,11,Frequest input from health, social care
OL,12,Fand social work professionals involved
OL,13,Fin the care of a patient when
OL,14,Fconsidering if a person is eligible
OL,15,Fand that Scottish Ministers can
OL,16,Fdetermine the level of training,
OL,17,Fqualification and experience a
OL,18,Fregistered medical practitioner or
OL,19,Fregistered nurse must have.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
