OL,5,CBills
OL,7,F'I am confident that these measures
OL,8,Fwill reassure clinicians that the
OL,9,FBill, which offers the choice that a
OL,10,Fsmall number of terminally ill Scots
OL,11,Fdesperately need, puts in place not
OL,12,Fonly greater compassion and choice but
OL,13,Falso more safety and protection that
OL,14,Fexists now."
OL,16,FMs Leadbeater has been contacted for
OL,17,Fcomment.
